    <note>Zhao(1) Zhan(2) [20956] He was selected for office through the baxing system in Daguan, but was ashamed to be reruited by a system devised by Cai(1) Jing [1649] and did not go. Later, he helped in the resistence against Fang(1) La [3298] and died. The county residents erected a shrine in order to pray to him. See also documentation of his father-in-law, Shen(2) Du(2) [20937]. SYXA, 32.656. CBD, 4, 3366-7.</note>
